| F-11 | New skill | `utility-pm-skill-iterate` (`/pm-skill-iterate`) . apply feedback, validation results, or convention changes to improve an existing skill | Claude | Planned | [#122](https://github.com/product-on-purpose/pm-skills/issues/122) |
