## Dependency Chain

```
F-05 (v2.7.0, shipped)
  ├── F-10 (validate) . checks against conventions F-05 established
  │     └── F-11 (iterate) . consumes validation reports from F-10
  └── M-12 (v2.7.0, shipped) . CI rules that F-10 mirrors at deeper level
```

F-10 should be built first. F-11 depends on F-10's output format (validation report) as one of its input types. D-03 can be drafted in parallel but finalized after both skills ship.

